{"tid":273044,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番]末日時在做什麼 第9話","createTime":"2017-06-06T09:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T23:50:55.000Z","uid":9024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55bf29b394e63a4365614b95cbee03af578205f0","tid":273044,"uid":9024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sukasuka-anime.com/core_sys/images/main/top/main_chara1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsukasuka-anime.com%2Fcore_sys%2Fimages%2Fmain%2Ftop%2Fmain_chara1.png&h=e0d56b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n除了獨自從數百年沉眠中甦醒的青年 威廉以外，人類遭到非比尋常的「獸」蹂躪而滅亡。唯有使用聖劍的妖精兵能代替人類打倒「獸」，但用盡力量的妖精兵們卻會殞命。<br />\n<br />\n「至少，我也希望自己不用消失，也想讓別人記住。我也想留下羈絆啊。」<br />\n<br />\n這是註定赴死的妖精少女們和青年教官共度的，既短暫又燦爛的日子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直播如有：00:05<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.bilibili.com/368444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.bilibili.com%2F368444&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1fffae56\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.bilibili.com/368444</a><br />\n<br />\n漫畫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cartoonmad.com/comic/5496.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cartoonmad.com%2Fcomic%2F5496.html&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ecac9c80\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cartoonmad.com/comic/5496.html</a><br />\n<br />\n動畫<br />\n<br />\n中文字幕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42304-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-42304-1-1.html&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8770d30e\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42304-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n無字幕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://up.b9dm.com/index.php/playlist/view/4604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fup.b9dm.com%2Findex.php%2Fplaylist%2Fview%2F4604&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=17831517\" target=\"_blank